_Sanjana Hattotuwa_ 於 _ICT For Peacebuilding（ICT4Peace）_
上[討論](http://ict4peace.wordpress.com/2010/03/29/citizens-net-crowd-sourcing-
human-rights-violations/ "http://ict4peace.wordpress.com/2010/03/29/citizens-
net-crowd-sourcing-human-rights-violations/")斯里蘭卡 _公民網（Citizens Net）_
新群眾外包計畫的無國界本質。這項地圖計畫記錄了「性別暴力、兒童、老年人和殘障人士權利」等違反人權的議題。

